Sales Manager
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/04/29 07:28:33
Ref. JB3045323
Job Description
•	To be responsible for managing customer relations, directing the sales activities in Dubai.
•	To be responsible for providing requirements in time in order to increase sales performans.
•	Identify and meet with potential new customers to develop new business opportunities.
•	To develop sales startegy to satisfy business plan to be able to maximize sale opportunities within the market.
•	To prepare sales forecasts
and controls expenses in line with the budget.
Skills
•	Preferably having at least 5 years of marketing and sales experience in the FMCG / Food sector (Key Account experience preferable)
•	Excellent problem solving and decision making ability
•	Excellent interpersonal skills
•	Dynamic and leadership personality
•	Prensentable
•	Fluent in English (spoken and written) (Arabic preferable)
•	Having valid and clear driving licence
•	Be willing to travel on a regular basis in the country and in abroad
•	Working knowlegde of MS Office computer applications
Education
Business Administration, Management, Economics, Marketing
or
relevant degree
